  "mainHtml": "\n<section class=\"supplement-hero\"><div class=\"container supplement-hero-inner\"><div><div class=\"breadcrumb\"><a href=\"/\">首页</a><span>/</span><a href=\"/resources\">资源中心</a><span>/</span><b>材料手册</b></div><h1>加工材料选择手册</h1><p>从强度、重量、耐腐蚀、温度、外观和成本角度快速筛选常见金属与工程塑料。</p><div class=\"supplement-tags\"><span>铝合金</span><span>不锈钢</span><span>铜合金</span><span>工程塑料</span></div></div><img alt=\"加工材料选择\" src=\"/precision/insight-material.jpg\"/></div></section>\n<section class=\"supplement-section\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"supplement-title\"><h2>材料快速判断</h2><p>本页用于前期选材参考，具体牌号、性能和合规要求需以项目图纸、供应材料和测试结果为准。</p></div><div class=\"supplement-grid\"><article class=\"supplement-card\"><h3>铝合金</h3><p>重量低、加工性好，常用于支架、壳体、散热和结构样件。</p></article><article class=\"supplement-card\"><h3>不锈钢</h3><p>强度和耐腐蚀表现稳定，适合连接件、设备部件和耐磨结构。</p></article><article class=\"supplement-card\"><h3>工程塑料</h3><p>适合绝缘、轻量和低摩擦场景，需关注温度、刚性和尺寸稳定性。</p></article></div></div></section>\n<section class=\"supplement-section soft\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"supplement-title\"><h2>选材问题清单</h2></div><div class=\"process-list\"><div class=\"process-step\"><b>01</b><div><strong>零件承受什么载荷？</strong><span>拉伸、冲击、磨损、温度和疲劳会影响材料选择。</span></div></div><div class=\"process-step\"><b>02</b><div><strong>环境是否有腐蚀或绝缘要求？</strong><span>潮湿、化学介质、电气隔离和户外环境需要提前说明。</span></div></div><div class=\"process-step\"><b>03</b><div><strong>是否需要表面处理？</strong><span>阳极氧化、电镀、喷涂、钝化等会影响外观、尺寸和周期。</span></div></div></div></div></section>\n<section class=\"supplement-section\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"audit-box\"><h3>选材确认要点</h3><div class=\"review-list\"><span>牌号与规格</span><span>强度与温度条件</span><span>表面与检测要求</span><span>成本与采购周期</span></div></div></div></section>\n"
}
